ility \"pockets\" where the average\nelectronic probability is substantially smaller than 1/2.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Sep 1998 21:36:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Nov 1998 15:29:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
