\nof the cohomological field theory related to Witten's conjecture (see\nmath.AG/9905034).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Sep 1998 22:29:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Oct 1998 23:07:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 8 Jul 1999 23:31:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-25"}
